	"transcription": [
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:00,000",
				"to": "00:00:06,320"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 0,
				"to": 6320
			},
			"text": " The Florida Everglades stretch across millions of acres of slow moving water and dense sawgrass."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:06,320",
				"to": "00:00:13,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 6320,
				"to": 13800
			},
			"text": " It is a highly specialized ecosystem, but right now, there is a massive predator moving just beneath the surface."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:13,800",
				"to": "00:00:20,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 13800,
				"to": 20800
			},
			"text": " 15 federal, state, and tribal agencies are currently operating under a single unified control plan."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:20,800",
				"to": "00:00:26,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 20800,
				"to": 26800
			},
			"text": " They are responding to a biological invasion that is actively dismantling the region's native wildlife."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:26,800",
				"to": "00:00:31,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 26800,
				"to": 31600
			},
			"text": " This is a sustained campaign against a masterfully adapted biological invader."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:31,600",
				"to": "00:00:37,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 31600,
				"to": 37400
			},
			"text": " The situation has evolved into a long-term struggle to preserve the Everglades remaining biodiversity."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:37,400",
				"to": "00:00:40,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 37400,
				"to": 40600
			},
			"text": " The crisis traces back to the 1970s and 80s."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:40,600",
				"to": "00:00:45,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 40600,
				"to": 45200
			},
			"text": " Miami had established itself as a booming hub for the global exotic pet trade,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:45,200",
				"to": "00:00:48,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 45200,
				"to": 48600
			},
			"text": " importing thousands of foreign reptiles into the United States."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:48,600",
				"to": "00:00:53,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 48600,
				"to": 53000
			},
			"text": " Consumers purchased young snakes, often unprepared for their rapid growth."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:53,000",
				"to": "00:00:57,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 53000,
				"to": 57800
			},
			"text": " Once these reptiles reached lengths of 10 feet or more and outgrew their enclosures,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:57,800",
				"to": "00:01:01,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 57800,
				"to": 61800
			},
			"text": " many owners illegally released them into the nearby swamps."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:01,800",
				"to": "00:01:04,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 61800,
				"to": 64600
			},
			"text": " Those localized releases seeded the wetlands."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:04,600",
				"to": "00:01:10,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 64600,
				"to": 70800
			},
			"text": " However, the primary catalyst for the current population explosion arrived in August of 1992,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:10,800",
				"to": "00:01:15,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 70800,
				"to": 75200
			},
			"text": " a Category 5 storm, Hurricane Andrew, tore through South Florida."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:15,200",
				"to": "00:01:18,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 75200,
				"to": 78400
			},
			"text": " The winds destroyed a specific python breeding facility,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:18,400",
				"to": "00:01:23,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 78400,
				"to": 83000
			},
			"text": " releasing hundreds of snakes directly into the surrounding swamps all at once."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:23,000",
				"to": "00:01:26,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 83000,
				"to": 86600
			},
			"text": " For years, researchers treated sightings as isolated incidents."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:26,600",
				"to": "00:01:28,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 86600,
				"to": 88600
			},
			"text": " That changed in the year 2000,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:28,600",
				"to": "00:01:34,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 88600,
				"to": 94200
			},
			"text": " when scientists officially recognized the pythons as an established, reproducing population in the wild."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:34,200",
				"to": "00:01:39,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 94200,
				"to": 99000
			},
			"text": " Confirming a self-sustaining population marks a critical threshold for an invasive species."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:39,000",
				"to": "00:01:41,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 99000,
				"to": 101600
			},
			"text": " At this stage, prevention is no longer possible,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:41,600",
				"to": "00:01:45,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 101600,
				"to": 105600
			},
			"text": " and the state must shift resources toward active management and containment."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:45,600",
				"to": "00:01:49,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 105600,
				"to": 109400
			},
			"text": " The Burmese python possesses severe biological advantages in Florida."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:49,400",
				"to": "00:01:52,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 109400,
				"to": 112000
			},
			"text": " They have no natural predators here."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:52,000",
				"to": "00:01:56,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 112000,
				"to": 116000
			},
			"text": " Their cryptic coloration provides near-perfect camouflage in the brush,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:56,000",
				"to": "00:02:00,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 116000,
				"to": 120200
			},
			"text": " and a single female can produce up to 100 eggs per clutch."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:00,200",
				"to": "00:02:05,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 120200,
				"to": 125400
			},
			"text": " This graph tracks native mammal observations against the timeline of the python's expansion."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:05,400",
				"to": "00:02:11,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 125400,
				"to": 131600
			},
			"text": " Since 1997, observations of raccoons and opossums have collapsed by 99%."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:11,600",
				"to": "00:02:14,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 131600,
				"to": 134600
			},
			"text": " Bobcat sightings have dropped by 87%."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:14,600",
				"to": "00:02:17,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 134600,
				"to": 137200
			},
			"text": " For other species, the numbers have hit zero."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:17,200",
				"to": "00:02:20,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 137200,
				"to": 140600
			},
			"text": " Marsh rabbits and foxes are now considered locally extinct"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:20,600",
				"to": "00:02:24,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 140600,
				"to": 144400
			},
			"text": " across most areas where the pythons have successfully invaded."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:24,400",
				"to": "00:02:27,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 144400,
				"to": 147000
			},
			"text": " Because pythons are dietary generalists,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:27,000",
				"to": "00:02:29,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 147000,
				"to": 149600
			},
			"text": " they do not starve when small mammals disappear."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:29,600",
				"to": "00:02:33,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 149600,
				"to": 153200
			},
			"text": " They simply move up the food chain, successfully hunting and consuming"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:33,200",
				"to": "00:02:37,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 153200,
				"to": 157600
			},
			"text": " the region's native apex predators, including the American alligator."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:37,600",
				"to": "00:02:42,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 157600,
				"to": 162600
			},
			"text": " They also introduced a secondary invisible threat, an Asian lungworm parasite."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:42,600",
				"to": "00:02:47,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 162600,
				"to": 167600
			},
			"text": " It is now infecting and killing native Florida snakes that have no natural immunity to the pathogen."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:47,600",
				"to": "00:02:52,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 167600,
				"to": 172000
			},
			"text": " The python is actively unraveling the Everglades entire food web,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:52,000",
				"to": "00:02:55,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 172000,
				"to": 175400
			},
			"text": " removing prey and competing predators simultaneously."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:02:55,400",
				"to": "00:03:00,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 175400,
				"to": 180200
			},
			"text": " In response, Florida has mobilized civilian forces to manually clear the swamps,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:00,200",
				"to": "00:03:03,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 180200,
				"to": 183600
			},
			"text": " most notably through the annual Florida python challenge."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:03,600",
				"to": "00:03:08,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 183600,
				"to": 188400
			},
			"text": " Nearly one Gaussian participants travel from across the globe to compete in this 10-day event,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:08,400",
				"to": "00:03:12,200"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 188400,
				"to": 192200
			},
			"text": " hunting snakes for a chance at $10,000 in prize money."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:12,200",
				"to": "00:03:15,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 192200,
				"to": 195600
			},
			"text": " Between these civilian events and state-funded professional contractors,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:15,600",
				"to": "00:03:20,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 195600,
				"to": 200400
			},
			"text": " more than 23,000 pythons have been captured and removed from Florida's public lands."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:20,400",
				"to": "00:03:24,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 200400,
				"to": 204000
			},
			"text": " This visualization represents the scale of those removal efforts."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:24,000",
				"to": "00:03:28,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 204000,
				"to": 208600
			},
			"text": " These 23,000 removed snakes represent a tiny fraction of the total problem."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:28,600",
				"to": "00:03:34,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 208600,
				"to": 214400
			},
			"text": " As we zoom out, statistical estimates suggest we are catching less than 1% of the actual population."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:34,400",
				"to": "00:03:37,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 214400,
				"to": 217600
			},
			"text": " The python's camouflage makes it nearly invisible to the human eye,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:37,600",
				"to": "00:03:41,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 217600,
				"to": 221800
			},
			"text": " meaning brute force hunting alone cannot keep pace with the population growth."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:41,800",
				"to": "00:03:46,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 221800,
				"to": 226000
			},
			"text": " Scientists are now searching for a different way to find the snakes."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:46,000",
				"to": "00:03:51,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 226000,
				"to": 231000
			},
			"text": " Wildlife agencies have pivoted toward high-tech surveillance and biological tracking"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:51,000",
				"to": "00:03:53,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 231000,
				"to": 233800
			},
			"text": " to bypass the python's natural defenses."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:03:53,800",
				"to": "00:03:57,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 233800,
				"to": 237800
			},
			"text": " Under the scout snake program, researchers capture male pythons,"
